@startuml
title FSA 2026 — Autentifikačný flow (OAuth2 / OIDC)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam sequenceBoxBackgroundColor #F9F9F9
skinparam sequenceBoxBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #EEF4FF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #4A6FA5
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5

participant "Prehliadač\n(Angular FE)" as FE #FEF9E7
participant "ingress-nginx" as ING #EAF2FF
participant "Keycloak\n(/auth/...)" as KC #F5EEF8
participant "Backend\n(Spring Boot)" as BE #D5F5E3
participant "PostgreSQL\n(fsa-db)" as DB #FDEBD0

== Inicializácia — načítanie OIDC konfigurácie ==

FE -> ING : GET /auth/realms/fsa/.well-known/openid-configuration
ING -> KC : forward
KC --> FE : OIDC metadata\n(token_endpoint, jwks_uri, ...)

== Prihlásenie (Authorization Code Flow) ==

FE -> KC : redirect → /auth/realms/fsa/protocol/openid-connect/auth\n?client_id=FSA-client&response_type=code&redirect_uri=...
KC --> FE : Login stránka
FE -> KC : POST credentials  (email + heslo)
KC -> KC : overenie hesla\n(bcrypt hash)
KC --> FE : redirect → /callback?code=<auth_code>

FE -> KC : POST /token\nbody: code=<auth_code>&client_id=FSA-client
KC --> FE : access_token (JWT, 5 min)\nrefresh_token (JWT, 30 min)\nid_token

note right of FE
  access_token obsahuje:
  - sub (user ID)
  - email
  - realm_roles: [STUDENT / TEACHER / ADMIN]
  - exp (expirácia)
end note

== Autorizovaný API request ==

FE -> ING : GET /api/discussions\nAuthorization: Bearer <access_token>
ING -> BE : forward request + token
BE -> KC : GET /auth/realms/fsa/protocol/openid-connect/certs\n(iba pri štarte alebo cache miss)
KC --> BE : JWKS (public key pre overenie podpisu)
BE -> BE : lokálna JWT verifikácia\n(podpis + exp + rola)
BE -> DB : SELECT ... FROM discussion
DB --> BE : výsledky
BE --> FE : 200 OK + JSON

== Obnova tokenu (refresh) ==

FE -> KC : POST /token\ngrant_type=refresh_token&refresh_token=<token>
KC --> FE : nový access_token

note right of FE
  Angular interceptor automaticky
  refreshuje token pred každým
  volaním ak access_token expiroval
end note

@enduml
